metadata.title: Hydrography - 1:63360 (ITM1)

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Chugach National Forest

metadata.description: Data Type: Freshwater Systems;  The Basemap Project captures hydrographic information by USGS quadrangles at 1:63,360 scale for the Alaska Department of Natural Resources (ADNR). This information is used as base data for the state's graphic land records, known as status plats.
